      "title" : "The day you let 32 new artists crash your dancefloor",
      "description" : "From late evening through night, you cycled through Swedish House Mafia, The Blaze, and JVKE, then let “52 Bars” by Karan Aujla echo into the morning. Afternoon and evening brought a parade of new names—32 artists making their debut in your queue, from Afro house to indie electronic. 579 minutes, 166 tracks, 225 artists—your biggest discovery day all year.",
