      "description" : "From late evening through dawn, “STFU” by AP Dhillon and Shinda Kahlon spun on near-constant repeat—over 90 times, with only brief afternoon detours for “Old Money” and a few radio interludes. 410 minutes, 148 plays, 25 artists—your most AP Dhillon–dominated day of the year.",
